35 namespace Mutation {
36  namespace Transfer {
37 
38 class OmegaI : public TransferModel
39 {
40 
41 public:
42  OmegaI(Mutation::Mixture& mix)
43  : TransferModel(mix)
44  {
45  m_ns = mixture().nSpecies();
46  m_nr = mixture().nReactions();
47  mp_hf = new double [m_ns];
48  mp_h = new double [m_ns];
49  mp_rate = new double [m_nr];
50  mp_delta = new double [m_nr];
51  for(int i=0; i<m_nr; ++i) {
52  if ( (mix.reactions()[i].type() == Kinetics::IONIZATION_E)
53  || (mix.reactions()[i].type() == Kinetics::DISSOCIATION_E)
54  || (mix.reactions()[i].type() == Kinetics::ELECTRONIC_DETACHMENT_E)
55  || (mix.reactions()[i].type() == Kinetics::EXCITATION_E)
56  || (mix.reactions()[i].type() == Kinetics::ION_RECOMBINATION_E)
57  || (mix.reactions()[i].type() == Kinetics::RECOMBINATION_E)
58  || (mix.reactions()[i].type() == Kinetics::ELECTRONIC_ATTACHMENT_E) )
59  m_rId.push_back(i);
60  }
61  };
62 
63  ~OmegaI() {
64  delete [] mp_hf;
65  delete [] mp_h;
66  delete [] mp_rate;
67  delete [] mp_delta;
68  };
69 
84  double source()
85  {
86  // Get Formation enthalpy
87  mixture().speciesHOverRT(mp_h, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, mp_hf);
88 
89  // Get reaction enthalpies
90  std::fill(mp_delta, mp_delta+m_nr, 0.0);
91  mixture().getReactionDelta(mp_hf,mp_delta);
92 
93  // Get molar rates of progress
94  mixture().netRatesOfProgress(mp_rate);
95 
96  double src = 0.0;
97  int j;
98  for (int i = 0; i < m_rId.size(); ++i) {
99  j = m_rId[i];
100  src += mp_delta[j]*mp_rate[j];
101  }
102 
103  return (-src*RU*mixture().T());
104 
105  }
106 
107 private:
108  int m_ns;
109  int m_nr;
110  std::vector<int> m_rId;
111  double* mp_hf;
112  double* mp_h;
113  double* mp_rate;
114  double* mp_delta;
115 };
